-/*
-  Similar to sd_notify() but takes a format string.
-
-  Example 1: A daemon could send the following after initialization:
-
-     sd_notifyf(0, "READY=1\n"
-                   "STATUS=Processing requests...\n"
-                   "MAINPID=%lu",
